WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.000
The ocean is full of things to sort and classify!

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
We can group sea creatures by size, colour, and type.

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Sorting helps us understand patterns in marine life.

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
Each category tells us something special about ocean ecosystems.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Let's explore the mathematics of marine classification!